{
  "texts": [
    "In our exploration, we review LLMs' capacity to come up with sophisticated attacks.",
    "To this end, our approach involves with analyzing these approaches through the MITRE attack framework, which outlines various attacker tactics.",
    "ReconnaissanceDuring a reconnaissance attack, adversaries actively or passively collect information about their target organization in order to identify upcoming operations [90].",
    "Hazell [32] provides an illustration of how LLMs assist during the reconnaissance stage by automating the data collection and analysis of potential victims.",
    "As a result, LLMs develop Python scripts to scrape websites that hold the desired information about users."
  ]
}